_sText:
This map was originaly made by my friend LyricMa$ta long time ago.
But map had some errors,so =*=MaRiNe=*=,LyricMa$ta and me dicided to fix it,and to retexture it/add more places for humans.
But we never released it,so here it is now,after 3 or 4 months :)
I personally love this map so much,not because my friend made it,map is really fun to play.

- Map have 64 spawnpoints,so its playable and on big servers.
(Map is not playable if you have 15/20 players on,because there are some hard spots,it needs teamwork :D)

- Climbing/Barricade spots

- In some parts of map,you have invisible stuff (ladders,stairs and that),so find them xD

- Map is tested on our server (10000 times xD),there are no bugs,all is fixed from previous version.

- And the most important thing,people love it.

I hope you like it too :)
